related_questions.question: Why is it called Ocean State Job Lot?
related_questions.snippet: The name derives from Rhode Island's nickname, "The Ocean State", and from "Job Lot", which means a miscellaneous group of articles, especially when sold or bought together. Ocean State Job Lot first opened in 1977 as a single store in North Kingstown.
